#. REF: sc32.1
msgctxt "an1.31-40:32.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ dantaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is tamed, is so very beneficial as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.31-40:32.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, dantaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "A tamed mind is very beneficial.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:32.1.3"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.33" id="33"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:32.1.4"
msgid "33 "
msgstr "33 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.7, sc33.1
msgctxt "an1.31-40:33.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ aguttaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it’s not guarded, is so very harmful as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.31-40:33.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, aguttaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "An unguarded mind is very harmful.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:33.1.3"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.34" id="34"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:33.1.4"
