#. REF: sc35.1
msgctxt "an1.31-40:35.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ arakkhitaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it’s not protected, is so very harmful as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.31-40:35.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, arakkhitaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "An unprotected mind is very harmful.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:35.1.3"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.36" id="36"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:35.1.4"
msgid "36 "
msgstr "36 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc36.1
msgctxt "an1.31-40:36.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ rakkhitaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is protected, is so very beneficial as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.31-40:36.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, rakkhitaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "A protected mind is very beneficial.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:36.1.3"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.37" id="37"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:36.1.4"
msgid "37 "
msgstr "37 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc37.1
msgctxt "an1.31-40:37.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ asaṃvutaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it’s not restrained, is so very harmful as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.31-40:37.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, asaṃvutaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "An unrestrained mind is very harmful.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:37.1.3"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.38" id="38"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:37.1.4"
msgid "38 "
msgstr "38 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc38.1
msgctxt "an1.31-40:38.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ saṃvutaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is restrained, is so very beneficial as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.31-40:38.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃvutaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "A restrained mind is very beneficial.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:38.1.3"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.39" id="39"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:38.1.4"
msgid "39 "
msgstr "39 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc39.1
msgctxt "an1.31-40:39.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ adantaṃ aguttaṃ arakkhitaṃ asaṃvutaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is not tamed, guarded, protected, and restrained, is so very harmful as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.31-40:39.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, adantaṃ aguttaṃ arakkhitaṃ asaṃvutaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "An untamed, unguarded, unprotected, and unrestrained mind is very harmful.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:39.1.3"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.40" id="40"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:39.1.4"
