#. REF: sc40.1
msgctxt "an1.31-40:40.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ dantaṃ guttaṃ rakkhitaṃ saṃvutaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is tamed, guarded, protected, and restrained, is so very beneficial as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.31-40:40.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, dantaṃ guttaṃ rakkhitaṃ saṃvutaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "A tamed, guarded, protected, and restrained mind is very beneficial.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:40.1.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

